
get-object-torrent
******************


DESCRIPTION
===========

Return torrent files from a bucket.


SYNOPSIS
========

   aws s3 get-object-torrent
     --bucket <value>
     --key <value>
     output_file


REQUIRED PARAMETERS
===================

"--bucket"  (string)

"--key"  (string)


OPTIONAL PARAMETERS
===================

None


POSITIONAL ARGUMENTS
====================

"output_file"  (blob)
   The output file
